Package org.apache.jena.sparql.syntax.syntaxtransform

Class ElementTransformIdentity

java.lang.Object
org.apache.jena.sparql.syntax.syntaxtransform.ElementTransformIdentity
All Implemented Interfaces:
ElementTransform
public final class ElementTransformIdentity extends Object implements ElementTransform
Transformation function on an Element that does nothing. Do not extend - it assumes that no change below happens. Use ElementTransformCopyBase instead.
